Posts.Content: Hi sweetie .. I,m new here ... just found out my 'news' on weds of this week .. :( .. suspected ovarian cancer here .. I have so many thougths and feelings they are unreal ... I wish I knew what to say to you .. but I dont, .. all I can say is keep posting .. I dont think I have yet but I do in tend to .. I know I have been in to chat to some of the lovelies on here .. they are all so warm and welcoming .. they humble me so much .. I wish you all the best and will keep you in my thoughts and prayers .. Hugs as always x Eileen xx
